WEBVTT

00:01.067 --> 00:03.317
(THEME PLAYING)

00:22.656 --> 00:25.325
MAN: It's hot. Crazy hot.

00:25.392 --> 00:27.761
Face-of-the-sun hot.

00:27.828 --> 00:29.429
What are you doing?

00:29.496 --> 00:33.734
All the cold air
is getting out!

00:33.801 --> 00:35.370
WOMAN:
Mommy's running some errands.

00:35.436 --> 00:37.872
Do me a favor, Tom,
and stay out of Daddy's way.

00:37.938 --> 00:40.007
The heat makes him grumpy.

00:40.074 --> 00:43.310
MAN: I'm not that cat's Daddy!

00:43.377 --> 00:45.177
WOMAN: See?

00:53.521 --> 00:56.523
You're gonna have a pool
by the end of the day,
Tykey boy,

00:56.590 --> 00:58.692
if it's the last of me.

00:58.759 --> 01:00.259
(PANTING)

01:09.236 --> 01:10.303
(BARKS)

01:10.370 --> 01:13.540
(PANTING)

01:13.607 --> 01:16.277
(ICE CUBES RATTLING)

01:16.344 --> 01:20.314
MAN: It's too hot
to read the paper.

01:20.381 --> 01:25.381
SPIKE: (LAUGHS)
There it is, boy.
Your very own pool.

01:26.820 --> 01:31.157
(SLURPING)

01:31.224 --> 01:32.693
(GROWLS)

01:32.760 --> 01:35.228
Why, you're a...

01:35.295 --> 01:37.731
(TYKE WHIMPERS)

01:37.798 --> 01:39.233
So you know.

01:39.300 --> 01:42.502
Nothing good ever comes from
punching someone's lights out.

01:42.569 --> 01:44.170
Understand, Tykey boy?

01:44.237 --> 01:45.606
(BARKS)

01:45.672 --> 01:50.022
No matter how good it feels.

01:52.880 --> 01:54.481
(SNIFFING)

01:54.548 --> 01:56.416
(BEE BUZZING)

01:56.483 --> 02:00.854
(BARKS)

02:00.921 --> 02:03.291
MAN: Ah, where's that fan?

02:03.357 --> 02:06.394
Ugh! I can never find
anything around here.

02:06.461 --> 02:11.461
If I look downstairs,
it's upstairs.
If I look upstairs...

02:14.234 --> 02:16.034
(SHIVERING)

02:19.974 --> 02:24.878
(GROWLS)

02:24.945 --> 02:26.295
(UNZIPS)

02:32.486 --> 02:34.286
(SCREAMING)

02:56.409 --> 02:58.959
(JERRY LAUGHING)

03:02.016 --> 03:03.666
(SLURPING)

03:45.692 --> 03:47.942
(AIR WHOOSHING)

04:07.148 --> 04:10.148
(FAN POWERING DOWN)

04:12.953 --> 04:17.153
MAN: Look who found my fan.

04:19.427 --> 04:24.427
I suppose you had nothing
to do with this, eh, Tom?

04:29.770 --> 04:34.074
Meet the great outdoors, cat!

04:34.141 --> 04:36.677
(SCREECHES)

04:36.743 --> 04:38.846
(BIRD CALLING)

04:38.912 --> 04:41.414
(SIZZLING)

04:41.481 --> 04:42.981
(SCREAMS)

04:48.122 --> 04:49.922
(INAUDIBLE)

04:55.863 --> 04:57.764
(JERRY WHISTLES)

04:57.831 --> 04:59.481
(WHISTLES)

05:05.005 --> 05:06.355
(GRUNTS)

05:14.515 --> 05:19.515
So nice of you
to build Tyke's pool.

05:20.087 --> 05:24.024
We're on Step 1.
Start digging, boys.

05:24.091 --> 05:28.795
And I'm warning you both,
no funny business. You got me?

05:28.862 --> 05:30.664
That's what I wanna see.

05:30.731 --> 05:33.734
Happy digging!

05:33.800 --> 05:34.550
Dig!

05:45.145 --> 05:47.095
(TYKE BARKS)

05:55.523 --> 05:57.490
Oopsie! Didn't see
your face coming.

05:57.557 --> 05:58.592
(TYKE WHIMPERS)

05:58.658 --> 05:59.558
Sorry.

06:05.665 --> 06:06.565
Phew!

06:14.709 --> 06:19.709
Listen, cat. If you're
not helping, you're hurting.
Got it?

06:37.731 --> 06:39.381
(LAUGHING)

06:44.838 --> 06:48.642
(SCREAMING)

06:48.709 --> 06:49.676
(SHRIEKS)

06:49.743 --> 06:51.178
(BARKING)

06:51.245 --> 06:53.045
Good doggy!

07:12.632 --> 07:14.068
(COOING)

07:14.134 --> 07:15.836
SPIKE: Step 2, boys.

07:15.903 --> 07:19.240
That cement
should almost be ready.

07:19.306 --> 07:21.008
(BARKING)

07:21.075 --> 07:23.175
(BEE BUZZING)

07:33.754 --> 07:37.925
(SCREAMING)

07:37.991 --> 07:40.527
It won't be long, Tykey boy.

07:40.594 --> 07:43.997
Tyke?

07:44.064 --> 07:47.364
Have you seen my boy?

07:51.171 --> 07:54.908
Hang on, boy,
I'm coming for you!

07:54.975 --> 07:58.879
-(BARKS)
-(SCREAMS)

07:58.946 --> 08:01.796
(TEETH CHATTERING)

08:13.660 --> 08:17.564
(GROWLS)

08:17.631 --> 08:20.167
(KISSING)

08:20.234 --> 08:23.404
(GROWLS)

08:23.471 --> 08:26.006
(GRUNTING IN FRUSTRATION)

08:26.073 --> 08:30.677
(GROWLS)

08:30.744 --> 08:34.714
(YOWLING)

08:34.781 --> 08:36.216
(MEOWS)

08:36.283 --> 08:38.920
-SPIKE: Step 3, add water.
-(TAP SQUEAKS)

08:38.987 --> 08:43.987
Finish the diving board,
and Tyke is gonna be
one happy pup.

08:52.166 --> 08:53.966
(SPLASHING)

08:59.040 --> 09:02.976
(GROWLS) You got exactly
five seconds to finish
sanding that diving board!

09:03.043 --> 09:05.145
Or I'll use your face! Got it?

09:05.212 --> 09:07.914
(GROWLS)

09:07.981 --> 09:09.415
(GROANS)

09:09.482 --> 09:13.287
Please!

09:13.354 --> 09:17.991
(SIZZLING)

09:18.058 --> 09:19.793
(BLOWS)

09:19.860 --> 09:20.861
(SHRIEKS)

09:20.927 --> 09:22.727
(SCREAMING)

09:29.370 --> 09:31.020
Thank you.

09:34.808 --> 09:35.858
(YELLS)

09:45.452 --> 09:46.802
(GROWLS)

09:51.859 --> 09:55.662
Nothing like a refreshing dip
on a hot day, eh, Tyke?

09:55.729 --> 09:57.229
(BLOWING)

10:04.104 --> 10:06.173
(BEES BUZZING)

10:06.240 --> 10:09.042
There he is!

10:09.109 --> 10:12.146
(WHIMPERS)

10:12.212 --> 10:14.982
(GROWLING)

10:15.048 --> 10:19.753
(WHINES)

10:19.820 --> 10:20.870
(GULPS)

10:37.338 --> 10:41.642
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACH)

10:41.709 --> 10:46.209
-(KEYS JANGLE)
-(DOOR OPENS)

10:47.114 --> 10:51.614
Step 4, start all over again!

10:55.922 --> 10:57.256
(THEME PLAYING)
